    <p><b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="Get ready for some serious sticker shock if you want the new MacBook Pro's most-buzzed-about components and features."><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">如果要想得到最夯、最新的MacBook Pro部件和功能，就得做好准备，定价之高可谓让人瞠目结舌</code></b>.</p>
