  <li>
    <p><b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="Support for twice as much RAM (now up to 32GB)"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">支持双倍RAM（新产品最高可至32GB）  [使用as much]</code></b>.</p>
